{"tid":663500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"航母工程總指揮指國產航母屬世界頂級水平","createTime":"2018-05-13T10:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T09:07:41.000Z","uid":19552,"like":30,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"9278407f41f73a68a94c731b14b781aef468c5af","tid":663500,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T10:51:20.000Z","msg":"第一艘國產航母，早上七時許離開遼寧大連造船廠進行首次海試。國產航母在清晨5時30分鳴笛，之後發動機開始冒煙，大約1小時後，航母在拖船協助下離開碼頭泊位，之後再次鳴笛，並完成調頭，駛向外海。報道指，航母是前赴相關海域執行海上試驗任務，主要檢測驗證動力系統等設備的可靠性和穩定性，檢驗動力系統是不是達到設計要求，亦要驗測艦船速度、抗風浪性和武器裝備，海試周期一般是一年，實際時間根據測試情況。<br />\n<br />\n中船重工董事長、航母工程總指揮胡問鳴表示，國產航母將在遼寧艦的研制和使用基礎上更進一步，躋身世界先進航母行列，同時更將進一步完善中國的航母研發能力。胡問鳴又表示，現在中國有一支研發設計建造的隊伍，已經歷練成軍，而且平均年齡在36歲，將來國家想發展任何一型航母，都已具備自主設計能力。"},{"pid":"75645c35821216e76140f639e2c3c26fa6ca48c6","tid":663500,"uid":31098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T10:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd65fa37ab937989c0ec0438ac1ae38cc97b4412","tid":663500,"uid":86893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T10:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ef4122ed2cea6c433ec06bff37bcc7fc98f769","tid":663500,"uid":194,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T10:56:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/13/185614_0218e5705d85cde4900dbfa79e9c7241.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F13%2F185614_0218e5705d85cde4900dbfa79e9c7241.png&h=75b37fed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"