身世界先進航母行列，同時更將進一步完善中國的航母研發能力。胡問鳴又表示，現在中國有一支研發設計建造的隊伍，已經歷練成軍，而且平均年齡在36歲，將來國家想發展任何一型航母，都已具備自主設計能力。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T00:10:42.000Z","msg":"中船重工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你話blackwater就ja"},{"pid":"34bf8a78594f42d7b9a7edb62fcf0be61c172cdd","tid":663500,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T00:27:05.000Z","msg":"成班人係度睇少贏國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢講得出就一定有<br />\n之前隻核戰機都曝光左<br />\n我相信贏國已經秘密製造出高達<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74b54e0457febc20ace677795b31161c3c07397d","tid":663500,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T00:33:32.000Z","msg":"發動機冒煙<br />\n跳台起飛<br />\n世界頂級<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccbd78fb308b95064a4c1e92c6c5ad1c1990758c","tid":663500,"uid":183302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T00:40:05.000Z","msg":"佢同渡海小輪分別就係多幾支炮同多條跑道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d6ebd4124a0b65550b753b8bc20e08fa5397ed","tid":663500,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T00:56:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國產航母在清晨5時30分鳴笛，之後發動機開始冒煙</blockquote><br />\n睇到呢度笑撚左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b682be250b06ea94cb9f7d77e855f232289386f7","tid":663500,"uid":176637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9278407f41f73a68a94c731b14b781aef468c5af","tid":663500,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T10:51:20.000Z","msg":"第一艘國產航母，早上七時許離開遼寧大連造船廠進行首次海試。國產航母在清晨5時30分鳴笛，之後發動機開始冒煙，大約1小時後，航母在拖船協助下離開碼頭泊位，之後再次鳴笛，並完成調頭，駛向外海。報道指，航母是前赴相關海域執行海上試驗任務，主要檢測驗證動力系